{"tid":855858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉選舉捐款舞弊 李偲嫣遭廉署檢控","createTime":"2018-10-10T09:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T09:46:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5872f9d1645ea7a5dbf54505a1cc6a01adfb0cac","tid":855858,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BsPltMrRX_ymn6hSAQvfAQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/b21369dbc717dbbd24b81721764f2263\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBsPltMrRX_ymn6hSAQvfAQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fb21369dbc717dbbd24b81721764f2263&h=1f3f0fab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廉政公署今日(10日)落案起訴於2016年立法會換屆選舉中落敗的候選人李偲嫣，控告她涉嫌沒有遵從選舉法例處置某些選舉捐贈。被告將於周五(12日)在沙田裁判法院答辯。<br />\n<br />\n54歲的李偲嫣被控一項罪名，即在選舉中作出舞弊行為，沒有遵從《選舉（舞弊及非法行為）條例》第19（2）條處置某些捐款。<br />\n<br />\n被告於2016年7月24日公開宣布她有意在立法會換屆選舉的新界東地方選區參選，並於翌日向選舉事務處提交其就該選舉的提名表格。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指被告涉嫌於2016年7月24日至11月8日期間，在該選舉中作出舞弊行為，沒有遵從《選舉（舞弊及非法行為）條例》第19（2）條，即身為該選舉的候選人，在收取她不知道姓名／或地址的損贈者給予9項而每項1000港元以上合共22,530港元的選舉捐贈後，沒有確保該等捐贈不會用於償付或分擔償付她作為候選人的選舉開支；及將該等捐贈給予屬公共性質的慈善機構或慈善信託。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B6%89%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%8D%90%E6%AC%BE%E8%88%9E%E5%BC%8A%E3%80%80%E6%9D%8E%E5%81%B2%E5%AB%A3%E9%81%AD%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7-091701641.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%258D%2590%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E8%2588%259E%25E5%25BC%258A%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2581%25B2%25E5%25AB%25A3%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25BB%2589%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7-091701641.html&d=d%2F%2Bhen19C%2BT4pq%2BgCYCsjDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=1888a8e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B6%89%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%8D%90%E6%AC%BE%E8%88%9E%E5%BC%8A%E3%80%80%E6%9D%8E%E5%81%B2%E5%AB%A3%E9%81%AD%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7-091701641.html</a>"},{"pid":"377f6d3b64e5b077ae019a223090abd470e8eaa3","tid":855858,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:41:17.000Z","msg":"呢啲出圖做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c30ce938c1f7eabf09edd1d4ff3669e7b13016","tid":855858,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:43:23.000Z","msg":"梁振英：港人需要有奉獻精神<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bFhcJS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bFhcJS</a>"},{"pid":"a754cc795f3ee691821d779213df0860fb308cf8","tid":855858,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}